cards.title: Beresheet Hotel
cards.subtitle: A luxurious, serene getaway in the desert
cards.description: The Beresheet hotel in Mitzpe Ramon stands as a desert oasis that captures the rugged beauty of its surroundings. Perched on the edge of the breathtaking Ramon Crater, the hotel offers unparalleled panoramic views that inspire awe. Its unique architectural design and luxurious interiors seamlessly blend with the desert landscape, providing a harmonious and tranquil atmosphere. The hotel serves as a gateway to explore the natural wonders of the area, inviting guests to discover the allure of the Negev Desert while enjoying top-notch amenities and hospitality. Whether gazing at star-filled skies from the outdoor pool or embarking on desert adventures, the Beresheet hotel promises an unforgettable experience of both serenity and exploration.

cards.title: Nea spa & wellnes
cards.subtitle: A spa that have it all!
cards.description: Nea Spa is a haven of relaxation and rejuvenation, offering a serene escape from the demands of modern life. Located in a tranquil setting, the spa provides a range of luxurious treatments designed to nurture both the body and the mind. With its soothing ambiance, skilled therapists, and a comprehensive menu of therapies, Nea Spa ensures an indulgent experience tailored to each individual's needs. From invigorating massages to revitalizing skincare treatments, guests can immerse themselves in a world of pampering and self-care. Nea Spa's commitment to wellness and holistic healing makes it a destination where one can find solace, balance, and a renewed sense of well-being.

cards.title: Hudson Brasserie
cards.subtitle: Best meat restaurant in Town
cards.description: Hudson is an American-inspired meat restaurant. The menu includes a variety of cuts, burgers, sandwiches and a variety of classic dishes with a unique twist. Our raw materials are at the highest level, fresh and excellent and we try to let them “speak for themselves”. Our meat processing process is unique and uncompromising, the meats receive dedicated and meticulous care at our butchers.

cards.title: Paws & Whiskers Pet Spa
cards.subtitle: Pampering Pets with Love
cards.description: Paws & Whiskers Pet Spa is a luxurious grooming salon dedicated to giving your furry companions the ultimate pampering experience. Our professional groomers use gentle techniques and premium products to ensure your pets look and feel their best. From stylish haircuts to relaxing massages, we cater to both dogs and cats, making them feel loved and cherished during their spa day.

cards.title: Tom Greyhound
cards.subtitle: Unique clothes shop in Paris
cards.description: Tom Greyhound’s carefully curated selection of designers blends in perfectly within its sophisticated and elegant décor. The captivating use of space and volume allows several cultural codes to be combined.  At Tom Greyhound, the client doesn’t simply go from rack to rack. They are called to discover refined themes of apparel and accessories, which all stand out.  Tom Greyhound stages its identity: a store entirely dedicated to a multicultural and contemporary approach to fashion.

cards.title: Blossom Floral
cards.subtitle: Expressing Emotions with Flowers
cards.description: Blossom Florals is a boutique flower shop that creates stunning floral arrangements for every occasion. From romantic bouquets to elegant centerpieces, our skilled florists craft each arrangement with care and creativity. We source the freshest and most exquisite flowers to convey your emotions and add a touch of beauty to your special moments. Let Blossom Florals be your go-to destination for all things floral.

cards.title: Elva Pilates Studio
cards.subtitle: Come and feel your body
cards.description: Elva Pilates Studio in Norway is a haven for those seeking a holistic approach to fitness and well-being. Nestled in a serene setting, the studio offers a range of Pilates classes that focus on strengthening the body, improving flexibility, and promoting overall wellness. Led by experienced instructors, Elva Pilates Studio provides personalized guidance, ensuring that each session caters to individual needs and goals. With its emphasis on mindful movement and precise techniques, the studio helps clients achieve better posture, core strength, and a deeper mind-body connection. Whether you're a Pilates enthusiast or a newcomer, Elva Pilates Studio is the perfect place to embark on a journey towards a healthier and more balanced lifestyle in the beautiful Norwegian setting.

cards.title: Harmony Music Academy
cards.subtitle: Unleash Your Musical Talent
cards.description: Harmony Music Academy is a premier music school offering comprehensive music education for students of all ages. Our passionate instructors provide lessons in various instruments, including piano, guitar, violin, and voice. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced musician, we tailor our lessons to suit your skill level and musical interests. Join Harmony Music Academy and embark on a harmonious journey of music.

cards.title: Pnina Pie
cards.subtitle: Coffee and patisserie
cards.description: Pnina Pie Pastry is a delightful haven for pastry enthusiasts. This charming bakery, known for its delectable creations, crafts a wide array of mouthwatering pies and baked goods that tantalize the taste buds. From flaky, fruit-filled pies to savory options bursting with rich flavors, Pnina Pie Pastry offers a diverse selection to suit every palate. Their dedication to using quality ingredients shines through in every bite, making each pastry a delightful treat. Whether you're seeking a sweet indulgence or a savory delight, Pnina Pie Pastry is the go-to destination for a delightful culinary experience in Ashdod.

cards.title: Jules Vernes Glass Bottom Boat
cards.subtitle: Discover the underwater world
cards.description: Discover the underwater world of the Red Sea without getting your feet wet with this glass-bottom boat tour. Departing from Hananya Beach, travel in the comfort of a boat with all of the luxuries including shaded seating, a snack bar, and sun deck. Spot an array of underwater life such as different species of fish and coral.   Sail along the Gulf of Eilat in a 3-deck ship, with the lower deck located 2 meters underwater for optimal viewing. During your tour, see sights such as the Eilat Coral Reserve, the military port, and the Jordan border. Benefit from an informative commentary from the ship's captain along the way.
